4. cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) is a possible category as the paper proposes a feed-forward neural network model. 
5. cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is a less likely category as the paper does not deal with image or video data, but the model proposed in the paper could potentially be applied to tasks in computer vision.
